    "context": "\"Take between [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + \"]25%[/color] and [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + \"]50%[/color] less damage from piercing attacks, such as those from bows or spears\""
